We are looking for a Principal, Information Security to join our team at BNY Mellon.

 

Information Security: Ensures internal controls related to information security  management are sound and effective and drives the implementation of new controls. Assigned business/business partner areas are typically medium to large in size and moderately complex. Incumbents demonstrate a breadth of knowledge of information security  management best practices and a thorough understanding of control and security  management concepts.

 

Job Responsibilities:

Contribute to the establishment of information security  strategy for the business/business partner area and is responsible for ensuring the implementation of that strategy. Recognized as the information security  point of contact and subject matter expert within the assigned business/business partner areas;
Leverages security  control techniques to achieve business objectives. Contributes to the development and sustention of an information security -aware culture and mindset among employees, contractors and service providers;
Contribute to reducing the likelihood of negative reputational and regulatory due to non-compliance with the Banks information security  management policies and standards, including local procedures specific to the assigned business/business partner areas;
Build strategic relationships to influence at all levels of the organization. Liaises with other business units, operations, technology, legal and compliance staff. Collaborates with other stakeholders to develop and implement consensual decisions;
Support Information Security Awareness and Third-Party Governance activities in region.

 

Requirements:

Experience in dealing with highly sensitive and confidential information both internally and externally essential;
Solid experience in Information security;
Experience in financial services is preferred;
Fluency in English and Portuguese;
Desirable certification in Information Security or Information Systems Auditor;
Bachelor’s degree or equivalent combination of education and work experience required.

  

